text: A deleted scene is a scene removed from or replaced by another scene in the final version of a film or television series. It may also refer to: *Deleted Scenes (album), a 2012 album by Blueprint * Deleted Scenes (band), an American indie rock band * "Deleted Scenes", episode 58 of Aqua Teen Hunger Force * Deleted Scenes, a 2006 mini-album by Days in December
